ayed Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-ar|\u062c\u0627\u0645\u0639 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064a\u062e \u0632\u0627\u064a\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0628\u064a\u0631|}}\n|[[File:Front of Sheikh Zayed Mosque.jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|50000}}<ref name=\"SZGMC\">{{cite web|url=https://www.szgmc.gov.ae/en/theory-and-implementation|title=Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque in Abu Dhabi|last=|first=|date=31 January 2020|website=www.szgmc.ae|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915102746/http://www.szgmc.ae/|archive-date=15 September 2017|access-date=12 February 2019}}</ref>\n|{{nts|121800}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.halcrow.com/html/our_projects/projects/grand_mosque.htm|title=Sheikh Zayed Bin Sultan Al Nahyan Mosque \u2013 Abu Dhabi|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601072337/http://www.halcrow.com/html/our_projects/projects/grand_mosque.htm|archivedate=1 June 2009|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|[[Abu Dhabi]]\n|{{flag|United Arab Emirates}}\n|[[Persian architecture|Persian]], [[Mughal architecture|Mughal]], [[Moorish architecture|Moorish]]\n|2007\n|-\n|'''Baitul Jannat Jame Mosque'''\n|\n|{{nts|50,000}}<ref>{{cite web |title=First Juma prayers at largest mosque under construction at Bashundhara |url=https://www.daily-sun.com/arcprint/details/147069/First-Juma-prayers-at-largest-mosque-under-construction-at-Bashundhara/2016-06-25 |website=Daily Sun |accessdate=27 January 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n|50,000\n|[[Dhaka]]\n|{{flag|Bangladesh}}\n|[[Modern architecture|Modern]]\n|2020\n|-\n|'''[[Al-Markaz Al-Islami Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-id|Masjid Al-Markaz Al-Islami}}\n\n{{lang-bug|\u1a06\u1a14\u1a17\u1a01\u1a17 \u1a15\u1a12\u1a1b\u1a06\u1a11\u1a1b\u1a00 \u1a15\u1a12\u1a17\u1a14\u1a1b\u1a12\u1a06\u1a17}}\n|\n|{{nts|50000}}<ref>[http://makassar.tribunnews.com/2018/11/18/tribunwiki-profil-masjid-al-markaz-al-islami-dan-masjid-raya-arsitekturnya-bikin-takjub TRIBUNWIKI: Profil Masjid Al Markaz Al Islami dan Masjid Raya, Arsitekturnya Bikin Takjub] {{Webarchive|url=http