echnya inaugurates vast new mosque] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117033503/http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/17/us-russia-chechnya-mosque-idUSTRE49G41J20081017|date=17 November 2015}}, 17 October 2008, reuters.com, read 16 January 2015</ref>\n|\n|[[Grozny]]\n|{{flag|Russia}}\n|[[Ottoman architecture|Late Classical Ottoman]]\n|2008\n|-\n|'''[[Al-Azhar Great Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-id|Masjid Agung Al-Azhar}}\n|[[File:Masjid_Agung_Al-Azhar.jpg|center|160x160px]]\n|{{nts|10000}}<ref name=\":2\">[http://simas.kemenag.go.id/index.php/profil/masjid/60/ Masjid Agung Al Azhar] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213005525/http://simas.kemenag.go.id/index.php/profil/masjid/60/ |date=13 February 2019 }}. ''Kementerian Agama Republik Indonesia''. Retrieved 12 February 2019.</ref>\n|{{Nts|43,755}}<ref name=\":2\" />\n|[[Jakarta]]\n|{{flag|Indonesia}}\n|[[Minimalism]]\n|1958\n|-\n|'''[[Al-Ittihad Mosque Jatibarang]]'''\n{{lang-id|Masjid Al-Ittihad Jatibarang}}\n\n{{lang-jv|\ua9a9\ua9bc\ua9b1\ua9c0\ua997\ua9b6\ua9a2\ua9c0\ua984\ua9ad\ua9c0\ua986\ua9a0\ua9c0\ua9a0\ua9b6\ua9b2\ua9a2\ua9c0\ua997\ua9a0\ua9b6\ua9a8\ua9ab\ua981}}\n\n[[Jawi alphabet|Jawi]]: \u0645\u0633\u062c\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0627\u062a\u062d\u0627\u062f \u062c\u0627\u062a\u064a\u0628\u0631\u0627\u06a0\n|[[File:Al-Ittihad_Mosque.jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|10000}}<ref>[https://www.anugerahkubah.com/masjid-al-ittihad-jatibarang/ Masjid Al-Ittihad Jatibarang] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212190401/https://www.anugerahkubah.com/masjid-al-ittihad-jatibarang/ |date=12 February 2019 }}. ''PT Anugerah Kubah Indonesia''. Retrieved 12 February 2019.</ref>\n|\n|[[Brebes]]\n|{{flag|Indonesia}}\n|[[Javanese people#Architecture|Javanese]]\n|2008\n|-\n|'''[[Baitul Futuh Mosque]]'''\n|[[File:Baitul Futuh.jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|10000}}<ref name=\"Bait2016\">{{cite web|url=http://www.baitulfutuh.org/construction/|title=Baitul Futuh Mosque fact sheet|archiveurl=https://web.arc