, un monument religieux et architectural] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129021535/http://www.djazairess.com/fr/infosoir/103656 |date=29 November 2014 }} 30.08.2009, Retrieved 02.11.2011</ref>\n|{{nts|42000}}<ref name=\"anasr\" />\n|[[Batna, Algeria|Batna]]\n| {{flag|Algeria}}\n|[[Islamic architecture#Contemporary Islamic architecture|Contemporary Islamic]]\n|2003\n|-\n|'''[[Baiturrahman Grand Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-id|Masjid Raya Baiturrahman}}\n\n{{lang-ace|Meuseujid Raya Baiturrahman}}\n\n[[Jawi alphabet|Jawi]]: \u0645\u0633\u062c\u062f \u0631\u0627\u064a\u0627 \u0628\u064a\u062a\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u062d\u0645\u0646\n|[[File:Meuseujid_Raya.JPG|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|30000}}<ref name=\"imquirer\"/>\n|\n|[[Banda Aceh]]\n| {{flag|Indonesia}}\n|[[Indo-Saracenic Revival architecture|Indo-Saracenic Revival]], [[Mughal architecture|Mughal]], [[Moorish architecture|Moorish]]\n|1881\n|-\n|'''[[Imam Muhammad ibn Abd al-Wahhab Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-ar|\u0645\u0633\u062c\u062f \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0648\u0647\u0627\u0628|}}\n|[[File:Flickr - omar chatriwala - The State Mosque.jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|30000}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gulf-times.com/qatar/178/details/31543/state-mosque-to-be-named-after-imam-abdul-wahhab|title=State Mosque to be named after Imam Abdul Wahhab|work=Gulf-Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402114308/http://www.gulf-times.com/qatar/178/details/31543/state-mosque-to-be-named-after-imam-abdul-wahhab|archivedate=2 April 2015|url-status=live|accessdate=15 March 2015|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|[[Doha]]\n|{{flag|Qatar}}\n|[[Islamic architecture|Islamic]]\n|2010\n|-\n|'''[[Sabanc\u0131 Central Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-tr|Sabanc\u0131 Merkez Camii}}\n|[[File:Sabanci Merkez Camii.jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|28500}}<ref>[http://www.vaksa.org.tr/eng/?kalicieser/sos/adana/sabanci_merkez_cami/adana_sabanci_merkez_cami.html Official Sabanc\u0131 Foundation website] {{webarchive|url