a Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-ms|Masjid Putra}}\n\n[[Jawi alphabet|Jawi]]: \u0645\u0633\u062c\u062f \u06a4\u0648\u062a\u0631\u0627\n\n{{lang-zh|c=\u5e03\u7279\u62c9\u6e05\u771f\u5bfa|s=|t=|Masjid Dian Al-Mahri}}\n\n{{lang-ta|\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bbe \u0bae\u0b9a\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bbf}}\n|[[File:Masjid_Putra_Putrajaya_Dec_2006_002.jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|15000}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Putra Mosque|url=http://www.tourism.gov.my/en/my/web-page/places/states-of-malaysia/putrajaya/putra-mosque|work=Tourism Malaysia|accessdate=25 May 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525200728/http://www.tourism.gov.my/en/my/web-page/places/states-of-malaysia/putrajaya/putra-mosque|archive-date=25 May 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|\n|[[Putrajaya]]\n|{{flag|Malaysia}}\n|[[Modern architecture|Modern]], [[Mamluk architecture|Mamluk]], [[Moorish architecture|Moorish]]\n|1997\n|-\n|[[Grand Mosque (Kuwait)|'''Grand Mosque''']]\n{{lang-ar|\u0627\u0644\u0645\u0633\u062c\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0628\u064a\u0631|}}\n|[[File:Grand Mosque (Kuwait).jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|13000}}<ref>[https://www.booking.com/landmark/kw/grand-mosque.html Grand Mosque] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213005735/https://www.booking.com/landmark/kw/grand-mosque.html |date=13 February 2019 }}. ''Booking.com''. Retrieved February 12, 2019.</ref>\n|\n|[[Kuwait City]]\n|{{flag|Kuwait}}\n|[[Islamic architecture|Islamic]]\n|1986\n|-\n|'''[[Grand Mosque of Bandung]]'''\n{{lang-id|Masjid Raya Bandung}}\n\n{{lang-su|{{sund|\u1b99\u1b9e\u1baa\u1b8f\u1ba4\u1b93\u1baa \u1b9b\u1b9a \u1b98\u1b94\u1baa\u1b93\u1ba5\u1b80}}}}\n|[[File:Great Mosque of Bandung.jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|13000}}<ref>[http://yahala-int.com/en/tourist_area/151 Masjid Raya Bandung] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213005613/http://yahala-int.com/en/tourist_area/151 |date=13 February 2019 }}. ''Yahala''. Retrieved February 12, 2019.</ref>\n|\n|[[Bandung]]\n|{{flag|Indonesia}}\n|[[Arab Architecture|Arabian]], [[Architecture of Indonesia|Sundanese]]\n|2003\n|-\n|'''[[Uganda National Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-sw|Msikiti wa Taifa wa Uganda}}\n|[[File:Laika ac Gaddafi National Mosque, Kampala (6693328097).jpg|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|12200}}<ref>[http://www.ugpulse.com/travel-and-tourism/new-mosque-redraws-kampala-s-skyline/482/ug.aspx New Mosque Redraws Kampala's Skyline] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117003137/http://www.ugpulse.com/travel-and-tourism/new-mosque-redraws-kampala-s-skyline/482/ug.aspx |date=17 November 2018 }}. ''UGPulse''. Retrieved February 12, 2019.</ref>\n|\n|[[Kampala]]\n|{{flag|Uganda}}\n|[[Islamic architecture|Islamic]]\n|1972\n|-\n|'''[[Kota Kinabalu City Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-ms|Masjid Bandaraya Kota Kinabalu}}\n\n[[Jawi alphabet|Jawi]]: \u0645\u0633\u062c\u062f \u0628\u0646\u062f\u0627\u0631\u0627\u064a\u0627 \u0643\u0648\u062a\u0627 \u06a9\u0648\u062a\u0627 \u06a9\u064a\u0646\u0627 \u0628\u0627\u0644\u0648\n\n{{lang-zh|c=\u4e9a\u5e87\u5e02\u6e05\u771f\u5bfa|s=|t=|Masjid Dian Al-Mahri}}\n\n{{lang-ta|\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0bae\u0b9a\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bbf}}\n|[[File:KotaKinabalu Sabah CityMosque-05.jpg|center|160x160px]]\n|{{nts|12000}}<ref name=\"SM\">{{cite journal|work=Suara Masjid |language=Malay |title=Masjid Bandaraya, Kota Kinabalu |trans-title=City Mosque, Kota Kinabalu |date=October 2008 |issn=1511-9149 |issue=59 |volume=7  |url=http://www.islamgrid.gov.my/majalah/suaramasjid/SM59.pdf |page=7|archivedate=23 March 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323075435/http://www.islamgrid.gov.my/majalah/suaramasjid/SM59.pdf}}</ref>\n|\n|[[Kota Kinabalu]]\n|{{flag|Malaysia}}\n|[[Modern architecture|Modern]]\n|2000\n|-\n|'''[[Mosque of Rome]]'''\n{{lang-it|Moschea di Roma}}\n|[[File:Grande Mosqu\u00e9e de Rome.JPG|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|12000}}<ref>[http://www.prolocoroma.it/moschea-di-roma-centro-islamico-culturale/ Moschea di Roma] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212202136/http://www.prolocoroma.it/moschea-di-roma-centro-islamico-culturale/ |date=12 February 2019 }}. ''Pro Loco Roma Capitale''. Retrieved February 12, 2019.</ref>\n|{{nts|30000}}\n|[[Rome]]\n|{{flag|Italy}}\n|[[Islamic architecture|Islamic]]\n|1995\n|-\n|'''[[Akhmad Kadyrov Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-ru|\u041c\u0435\u0447\u0435\u0442\u044c \u0410\u0445\u043c\u0430\u0442\u0430 \u041a\u0430\u0434\u044b\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430}}\n\n{{lang-ce|\u041a\u0430\u0434\u044b\u0440\u043e\u0432 \u0410\u0445\u044c\u043c\u0430\u0434\u0430\u043d \u0446\u04c0\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0445 \u0434\u0438\u043d\u0430 \u043c\u0430\u044c\u0436\u0434\u0438\u0433}}\n|[[File:\u0413\u0440\u043e\u0437\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u043c\u0435\u0447\u0435\u0442\u044c 2011.JPG|160px|center]]\n|{{nts|10000}}<ref>[https://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/17/us-russia-chechnya-mosque-idUSTRE49G41J20081017 Russia's Chechnya inaugurates vast new mosque] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117033503/http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/17/us-russia-chechnya-mosque-idUSTRE49G41J20081017|date=17 November 2015}}, 17 October 2008, reuters.com, read 16 January 2015</ref>\n|\n|[[Grozny]]\n|{{flag|Russia}}\n|[[Ottoman architecture|Late Classical Ottoman]]\n|2008\n|-\n|'''[[Al-Azhar Great Mosque]]'''\n{{lang-id|Masjid Agung Al-Azhar}}\n|[[File:Masjid_Agung_Al-Azhar.jpg|center|160x160px]]\n|{{nts|10000}}<ref name=\":2\">[http://simas.kemenag.go.id/index.php/profil/masjid/60/ Masjid Agung Al Azhar] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213005525/http://simas.kemenag.go.id/index.php/profil/masjid/60/ |date=13 February 2019 }}. ''Kementerian Agama Republik Indonesia''. Retrieved February 12, 2019.</ref>\n|{{Nts|43,755}}<ref name=\":2\" />\n|[[Jakarta]]\n|{{flag|Indonesia}}\n|[[Minimalism]]\n|1958\n|-\n|'''[[Al-Ittihad Mosque Jatibarang]]'''\n{{lang-id|Masjid Al-Ittihad Jatibarang}}\n\n{{lang-jv|\ua9a9\ua9bc\ua9b1\ua9c0\ua997\ua9b6\ua9a2\ua9c0\u